Package: Bookdown2Donoda
Type: Package
Title: Compile bookdown formatted markdown to a Dodona-ready format
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Viktor Verstraelen
Maintainer: Lieven Clement <lieven.clement@ugent.be>
Description: The Bookdown2Dodona package can be used to compile a set of Rmarkdown files 
  that follow the bookdown standard to a folder structure of description files that can be directly used with Dodona.
License: LGPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.1)
Imports:
    dplyr,
    stringr,
    yaml,
    jsonlite,
    bookdown
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
